1279	### 8.4 Track Folding and Grouping
1280	
1281	Folder tracks contain subtracks and can be collapsed to a single row:
1282	
1283	```typescript
1284	interface FolderTrack {
1285	  id: string;
1286	  name: string;
1287	  collapsed: boolean;
