You are implementing E11-T1 for a DAW project: MIDI note data model, store extensions, and undo commands.

Tests have already been written and are failing. You need to make them pass by implementing the actual code.

## What to implement

### 1. Update `src/state/track/types.ts`

The current file has:
```typescript
export type TrackType = "audio" | "instrument";
export type TrackModel = { ... };
export type ClipModel = {
  readonly id: string;
  readonly trackId: string;
  readonly sourceId: string;
  readonly startTime: number;
  readonly sourceOffset: number;
  readonly duration: number;
  readonly gain: number;
  readonly fadeIn: number;
  readonly fadeOut: number;
