Change the `openNotes` map key from just `note` to `channel * 128 + note`:
```typescript
// note-on:
const key = message.channel * 128 + message.note;
openNotes.set(key, { ... });

// note-off:
const key = message.channel * 128 + message.note;
const open = openNotes.get(key);
```

